Class ConfSerializerV7

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.genesyslab.platform.configuration.protocol.runtime.channel.ConfSerializer

    public class ConfSerializerV7
extends ConfSerializer
    Configuration Protocol data serializer for 'V7' packing format.
    This format is used for transportation of configuration objects information.
